# Agent Creation Patterns

When creating or modifying agents in `mycosoft_mas/agents/`:

## Required Pattern

1. Inherit from `BaseAgent`
2. Constructor: `__init__(self, agent_id: str, name: str, config: Dict[str, Any])`
3. Call: `super().__init__(agent_id=agent_id, name=name, config=config)`
4. Use async methods for task processing
5. Include type hints on all methods

## Checklist After Creating an Agent

- [ ] Agent file created in `mycosoft_mas/agents/`
- [ ] Import added to `mycosoft_mas/agents/__init__.py`
- [ ] Class added to `__all__` list in `__init__.py`
- [ ] Agent registered in `docs/SYSTEM_REGISTRY_FEB04_2026.md`
- [ ] No mock data used -- real service connections only
